Descriptor, bir attribute'a erisim yoneten protokoldur (__get__, __set__, __delete__).

```python
class Validator:
    def __init__(self, min_value, max_value):
        self.min_value = min_value
        self.max_value = max_value

    def __set_name__(self, owner, name):
        self.name = name
        self.private_name = f'_{name}'

    def __get__(self, obj, objtype=None):
        if obj is None:
            return self
        return getattr(obj, self.private_name, None)

    def __set__(self, obj, value):
        if not self.min_value <= value <= self.max_value:
            raise ValueError(f'{self.name} {self.min_value}-{self.max_value} arasinda olmali')
        setattr(obj, self.private_name, value)

class Person:
    age = Validator(0, 150)
    salary = Validator(0, 1000000)

    def __init__(self, name, age, salary):
        self.name = name
        self.age = age
        self.salary = salary

p = Person('Ali', 30, 50000)
# p.age = 200  # ValueError!
```

gRPC, Google tarafindan gelistirilen RPC (Remote Procedure Call) framework'udur.

REST vs gRPC:
- REST: HTTP/1.1, JSON, text tabanli
- gRPC: HTTP/2, Protocol Buffers, binary tabanli

Avantajlari:
- Daha hizli (binary serialization)
- Streaming destegi
- Kod olusturma (proto dosyasi)
- Multi-dil destegi

Proto dosyasi:
```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";

service UserService {
  rpc GetUser (UserRequest) returns (UserResponse);
  rpc ListUsers (Empty) returns (stream UserResponse);
}

message UserRequest {
  int32 id = 1;
}

message UserResponse {
  int32 id = 1;
  string name = 2;
}
```

